<section class="hero">
    <div class="tagline">A soft return to yourself</div>
    <h1>Gentle, soul-deep healing for women in tender seasons.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
        Somatic, breath-centered, nervous-system–informed yoga therapy for women navigating
        grief, anxiety, emotional exhaustion, and life's quiet thresholds.
    </p>
    <div class="btn-row">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn">Book a Discovery Call</a>
        <a href="/yoga-therapy" class="btn btn-outline">Explore Yoga Therapy</a>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-cream">
    <div class="container narrow" style="text-align:center;">
        <div class="section-heading">
            <span class="eyebrow">Welcome</span>
            <h2>Bridging holistic healing with traditional care.</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
            Soul Deep Yoga Therapy uses the principles of yoga to support women through life's
            transitions, chronic pain, and loss—helping you rediscover health, balance, and a
            deep sense of wholeness.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you've spent years caring for others while navigating your own challenges, you
            deserve a space to soften, breathe, and be cared for too. Through breath, movement,
            and gentle somatic practices, we create a space where your nervous system can unwind
            and your whole being can exhale.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
