            <h2>Soul-centered offerings</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">i.</div>
                <h3>Yoga Therapy</h3>
                <p>
                    A clinical, personalized approach to healing that addresses physical,
                    emotional, and nervous system patterns through movement, somatics, and
                    breathwork.
                </p>
                <a href="/yoga-therapy">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">ii.</div>
                <h3>Private Yoga Sessions</h3>
                <p>
                    Deep Release, Deep Rest, Deep Breath—intentionally curated practices for
                    mobility, rest, and mindful breathing, tailored to you.
                </p>
                <a href="/yoga-therapy#private">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">iii.</div>
                <h3>The Mushroom Circle</h3>
                <p>
                    A 6-week private program blending microdosing integration support with
                    somatic healing, mindfulness, and grounded community.
                </p>
                <a href="/mushroom-circle">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-sage">
    <div class="container narrow" style="text-align:center;">
        <div class="section-heading">
            <span class="eyebrow">What is Yoga Therapy</span>
            <h2>A whole-person approach to healing.</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
            Yoga Therapy blends functional movement, breathwork, somatic awareness, nervous
            system regulation, and trauma-informed guidance. Every session is tailored to your
            unique health story and guided by a Certified Yoga Therapist in a private or
            small-group setting.
        </p>
        <p>This is not a workout. It is a healing relationship.</p>
        <a href="/yoga-therapy" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">Learn More</a>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="container narrow">
        <div class="section-heading">
            <span class="eyebrow">Who This Work Supports</span>
            <h2>You may find a soft landing here if…</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="soft-list">
            <li>You are carrying grief, loss, or a tender chapter of transition</li>
            <li>You experience chronic pain, fatigue, or burnout</li>
            <li>Anxiety, overwhelm, or emotional exhaustion live in your body</li>
            <li>You feel disconnected from your intuition, voice, or breath</li>
            <li>You long to feel more grounded, clear, and at home in yourself</li>
            <li>You are curious about microdosing as a gentle path toward healing</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>

